        <updateDate>2021-07-07T14:00:25Z</updateDate>
        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><strong>Clean H2 Production Act</strong> </p> <p>This bill provides tax incentives for the production of clean hydrogen and for investment in clean hydrogen production facilities. Specifically, it allows a new business-related tax credit for the production of specified amounts of qualified clean hydrogen. The bill defines<em> qualified clean hydrogen</em> as hydrogen that is produced through a process that, as compared to hydrogen produced by steam-methane reforming of nonrenewable natural gas, achieves a percentage reduction in life cycle greenhouse gas emissions that is not less than 50%. </p> <p>The bill also expands the energy tax credit to include clean hydrogen production facilities.</p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
